{"word":"G3819 - πάλαι - pálai - pal'-ahee - Any while","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πάλαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>pálai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>pal'-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Any while"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"அப்பொழுதே, அதற்குள்ளே - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. of old"},{"paragraph":"2. long ago"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Probably another form for <a href=\"#/G3825 - πάλιν - pálin - pal'-in/3825\">G3825</a> (through the idea of <i>retrocession</i>); (adverbially) <i>formerly</i>, or (relatively) <i>sometime since</i>; (elliptically as adjective) <i>ancient:</i> - any while, a great while ago, (of) old, in time past."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3819 - πάλαι - pálai - pal'-ahee/3819\">G3819</a>, <a href=\"#/G3820 - παλαιός - palaiós - pal-ah-yos'/3820\">G3820</a>, <a href=\"#/G3821 - παλαιότης - palaiótēs - pal-ah-yot'-ace/3821\">G3821</a>, <a href=\"#/G3822 - παλαιόω - palaióō - pal-ah-yo'-o/3822\">G3822</a>"}]}